      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Baby Put The Gun Down</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Covered up with grime you started up to climb.</l>
          <l>When you fall you know you fucked it up this time.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Think you got it right? </l>
          <l>Well try to be polite or you'll end up all alone at night</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I've known you for so long and still I do it all so wrong.</l>
          <l>Baby put the gun down.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Drink until you cry and ask yourself</l>
          <l>Why can't you just let it go by?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Think you're in control? </l>
          <l>Well look deep down your soul</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
